invalid type: string "## Archetype Terms\n\n**4c Control**: A four-color control deck (often without red or without white) that leverages the best cards from multiple colors. Uses Uro, planeswalkers, and blue cantrips/countermagic. Also called 'Czech Pile' in some configurations. *(Related cards: Uro, Titan of Nature's Wrath, Force of Will, Swords to Plowshares. See also: Czech Pile, control, midr